==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Toret
<hw>Tor"et</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>A ring for fastening a hawk's leash
to the jesses; also, a ring affixed to the collar of a dog, etc.</def>
<mark>[Obs.]</mark> <rj><au>Chaucer.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Toreumatography</ent>⟦br⟧
